# Environment variables — PriceScout (standalone repo `E:\Projects\pricescout`)

Copy to `.env.local` for dev; production mirrors these on the VPS / hosting provider.

```
# Postgres (required for admin/auth once migrated)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:5432/pricescout_prod

# Session JWT — min 16 chars (generate random)
PS_SESSION_SECRET=

# Public site URL — used for Stripe redirects & canonical metadata
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3300

# Stripe live — checkout + webhook (082)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
STRIPE_PRICE_WEEK_PASS=
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO_MONTHLY=
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO_ANNUAL=
STRIPE_PRICE_FOUNDERS_LIFETIME=

# Tenant slug stamped into Checkout metadata / webhook reconciliation
DEFAULT_TENANT_SLUG=demo-thrift

# Optional observability (103)
SENTRY_DSN=

# Seed demo password override (optional)
SEED_DEMO_PASSWORD=demo-password!

# Comparable-sales APIs (083)
COMP_PROVIDER=auto
KEEPA_API_KEY=
EBAY_CLIENT_ID=
EBAY_CLIENT_SECRET=

# Transactional mail (operator sets on VPS)
RESEND_API_KEY=

# Playwright base URL override for e2e
PLAYWRIGHT_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3300
```
